        <h2>This Application sample uses</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Sample pages using ASP.NET Core MVC</li>
            <li>Theming using <a href="https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=398939">Bootstrap</a></li>
            <li>Azure <a href="https://github.com/Azure/azure-iiot-opc-vault-service">OPC Vault</a> as registration and certificate service</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>The OPC Vault service uses</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Azure <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/key-vault/">Key Vault</a> to safeguard cryptographic keys and secrets</li>
            <li>Azure <a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/services/cosmos-db/">Cosmos DB</a> as database service</li>
            <li>OPC Foundation <a href="https://github.com/OPCFoundation/UA-.NETStandard">OPC UA .Net Standard</a> Stack for OPC UA services</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
